21. šu-luh lugal-ŋa₂-ke₄ sa₂ bi₂-in-dug₄
#lem: šuluh[ritual cleansing]; lugal[king]; sa[equal]; dug[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=21

22. kan₄-na en₃ tar-tar-ra-a-ba lu₂ na-ma-ši-in-kur₉-re-en
#lem: kan[gate]; en[cvne]; tar[cut]; lu[person]; kur[enter]
#etcsl: line-id=22

23. ku₄-ku₄-da-ŋu₁₀-ne
#lem: kur[enter]
#etcsl: line-id=23

24. {ŋiš}gu-za gar₃-ba kug-sig₁₇ huš-a ŋar-ra lu₂ ma-an-de₆ tuš-a ma-an-dug₄
#lem: guza[chair]; gar[knob]; kugsig[gold]; huš[reddish]; ŋar[put]; lu[person]; de[carry]; tuš[sit (down)]; dug[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=24

25. a₂ aŋ₂-ŋa₂ lugal-ŋa₂-ke₄ i₃-gub-be₂-en nu-tuš-u₃-de₃-en bi₂-dug₄
#lem: a[arm]; aŋ[measure]; lugal[king]; gub[stand]; tuš[sit (down)]; dug[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=25

26. (1:2:1) gud niga (2:20:2) udu niga {ŋiš}banšur-ŋu₁₀ lu₂ ma-an-sa₂
#lem: n; gud[bull]; niga[fattened]; n; udu[sheep]; niga[fattened]; banšur[table]; lu[person]; sa[equal]
#etcsl: line-id=26

:26v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) 1
#lem: n
:26v.2.1: (#note: the same ms. has instead:#) 6
